      "role": "user",
      "content": "My bad, I didn't mean to get controversial. I'm just trying to build a data model for our analysts. I'm looking for the economic logic behind the risk assessment. Is the volatility you're referring to tied to things like shifts in local spending power, changes in school district stability, or just the general lack of a cohesive community identity during a transition? Just trying to understand the underlying metrics you're using.",
